commit.message:
8371205: AArch64: Remove unused cmpxchg* methods

Since JDK-8364406, the AArch64 macroAssembler method
cmpxchg_obj_header is no longer used. The method cmpxchgptr is used
by cmpxchg_obj_header however is not used by any other method so can
be removed alongside cmpxchgptr.
cmpxchgw is also unused and can be removed.
